<BaseLayout title="Roberto Guarneros - About Me">
  <div class="about-container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>💫 About Me</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        Hello, I'm <strong>Roberto Guarneros</strong>. I have two degrees: Aerospace Engineering and Network Engineering.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm passionate about creating innovative solutions that span hardware, firmware, and software.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've worked at the <strong>Nanosat Lab</strong> (software for the 3Cat-8 on-board computer) and collaborated with <strong>SEAT-CUPRA</strong> on solutions that streamline car development and reduce costs.
